TuneResultCount

Type: int
Modifiable: No

After the tuning tools has been run, this attribute reports the number of parameter sets that were stored. This value will be zero if no improving parameter sets were found, and its upper bound is determined by the TuneResults parameter.

For examples of how to query or modify attributes, refer to our Attribute Examples.
